Robert Morgan, chief investment 
strategist at Fulcrum Securities, talks about the outlook for a 
Greek default and the U.S. economy.   Morgan also discusses his investment strategy for energy, 
materials and health-care stocks. He speaks with Matt Miller, 
Lisa Murphy and Julie Hyman on Bloomberg Television's "Street 
Smart." (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 08:48
 